OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police take
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions off the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FUnder UK law, e-bike motors must cut
OL,8,Fout when a speed of 15.5mph is reached.
OL,10,FBut police are increasingly finding
OL,11,Fmany have been modified to reach much
OL,12,Ffaster speeds.
OL,14,FIt is also common for officers to find
OL,15,Fe-bikes that can be powered without
OL,16,Fthe pedals being turned, effectively
OL,17,Fmaking them electric mopeds or
OL,18,Fmotorbikes which must be registered
OL,19,Fand taxed.
