OL,7,FConversion kits are available online
OL,8,Ffor as little as #300.
OL,10,FCity of London Police recently seized
OL,11,Fan e-bike capable of reaching 70mph,
OL,12,Fwhich featured an electronic display
OL,13,Findicating it had covered more than
OL,14,F6,000 miles.
OL,16,FDuring another operation outside
OL,17,FLondon Liverpool Street railway
OL,18,Fstation earlier this month, it took
OL,19,Fofficers just minutes to catch a rider
OL,20,Fusing an illegal e-bike.
