OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police take
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions off the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FTwenty-seven out of 46 police forces
OL,8,Fprovided data in response to PA's
OL,9,FFreedom of Information requests.
OL,11,FAmong the forces with the largest year-
OL,12,Fon-year increases in e-bike seizures
OL,13,Fwere Wiltshire Police (from 24 to 64),
OL,14,FPolice Scotland (from 60 to 233),
OL,15,FDerbyshire Police (from four to 23),
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police (from 18 to 58) and
OL,17,FSouth Wales Police (from 66 to 137).
