OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police take
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions off the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FThese include City of London, which
OL,8,Falone confiscated 295 in the year to
OL,9,FAugust 11 ` more than all other forces
OL,10,Fthat provided data ` but could not
OL,11,Fissue a total for the previous 12
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FActing Sergeant Chris Hook, who is
OL,15,Fpart of the leadership team within the
OL,16,Fforce's cycle unit established in July
OL,17,F2023, explained that a "broad
OL,18,Fspectrum" of people ride illegally
OL,19,Fmodified e-bikes, such as commuters,
OL,20,Ffood delivery workers and criminals
OL,21,Fsnatching phones.
