OL,7,FThis "keeps them and the public safe",
OL,8,Fand going beyond that "doesn't feel
OL,9,Freasonable", he added.
OL,11,FTanya Braun, director of policy and
OL,12,Fcommunications at walking charity
OL,13,FLiving Streets, said illegally
OL,14,Fmodified e-bikes used on pavements
OL,15,F"pose the same danger and provoke the
OL,16,Fsame fear as a motorbike coming up
OL,17,Falongside a pedestrian".
